{% comment %}
  CUSTOMIZED: Dromgoole's Custom Header with Block-Based Layout
  Author: Dromgoole's
  Modified: 2025-12-23
  Original: Dawn v15.4.1

  Changes:
  - Block-based architecture allowing reordering of header elements (drawer, search, logo, account, cart)
  - Each element is a draggable block in the theme editor with position setting (left/center/right)
  - Account icon always visible on mobile (no small-hide class)
  - Simplified layout using three groups: left, center, right
{% endcomment %}

